{
  "texts": [
    "We believe more research is needed to align the outputs of these LLMs for such high-stake domains like healthcare where a single misinformation (or disinformation) could lead to drastic consequences.",
    "Jingjing Xu, Hao Zhou, et al. 2021.",
    "Vocabulary learning via optimal transport for neural machine translation.",
    "In Proceedings of the 59th Annual Meeting of the Association for Computational Linguistics and the 11th International Joint Conference on Natural Language Processing (Volume 1: Long Papers), pages 7361-7373, Online.",
    "Association for Computational Linguistics."
